---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title='Privacy Policy | Apex Corporate Solutions'>
    <section class='py-20 bg-background'>
        <div class='container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 max-w-3xl'>
            <h1 class='text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-2'>
                Privacy Policy
            </h1>
            <p class='text-muted-foreground mb-8'>
                Last Updated: 21 November 2025
            </p>

            <div
                class='prose prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-none space-y-8'
            >
                <p>
                    Apex Corporate Solutions, a trading division of Playhouse
                    Media Group (Pty) Ltd ("we," "us," or "our"), is committed
                    to protecting your personal information and your right to
                    privacy. This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use,
                    and share your personal information when you visit our
                    website (www.apexcorporate.co.za) or subscribe to our
                    digital infrastructure services.
                </p>

                <div>
                    <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-4'>
                        1. INFORMATION WE COLLECT
                    </h2>
                    <p class='mb-4'>
                        We collect personal information that you voluntarily
                        provide to us when you register for our services,
                        express an interest in obtaining information about us,
                        or contact us. The personal information we collect may
                        include:
                    </p>
                    <ul class='list-disc pl-6 space-y-2'>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Personal Details:</strong> Name, Surname, ID
                            Number (where applicable for domain registration).
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Contact Data:</strong> Email address, mobile
                            number, and physical address.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Business Data:</strong> Registered Company Name,
                            CIPC Registration Number, VAT Number.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Payment Data:</strong> We do not store credit
                            card details directly. Payment data is processed securely
                            by our third-party payment processor, Paystack.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-4'>
                        2. HOW WE USE YOUR INFORMATION
                    </h2>
                    <p class='mb-4'>
                        We use your personal information for the following
                        legitimate business purposes:
                    </p>
                    <ul class='list-disc pl-6 space-y-2'>
                        <li>
                            <strong>To facilitate account creation:</strong> To set
                            up your hosting account, register your domain name, and
                            provision your email services.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>To send administrative information:</strong>
                            To send you invoices, server status updates, and changes
                            to our terms or policies.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>To fulfill and manage your orders:</strong> To
                            manage your monthly subscription payments and renewals.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>To comply with legal obligations:</strong> For
                            example, the domain registry (ZACR) requires specific
                            contact information to be listed for any .co.za domain
                            owner.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-4'>
                        3. SHARING YOUR INFORMATION
                    </h2>
                    <p class='mb-4'>
                        We only share information with the consent of the data
                        subject, or where it is legally required for the
                        operation of our services. We share data with the
                        following trusted third-party vendors:
                    </p>
                    <ul class='list-disc pl-6 space-y-2'>
                        <li>
                            <strong>HostAfrica:</strong> Our upstream hosting provider.
                            Your website files and emails are stored on their secure
                            servers.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Paystack:</strong> Our payment gateway. They
                            process your debit/credit card transactions.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>ZACR (ZA Central Registry):</strong> The regulatory
                            body for .co.za domains. Your name and contact details
                            are required by them to register a domain in your name.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class='mt-4'>
                        We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information
                        to marketing agencies or other third parties.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-4'>
                        4. DATA SECURITY
                    </h2>
                    <p>
                        We have implemented appropriate technical and
                        organizational security measures designed to protect the
                        security of any personal information we process. This
                        includes SSL encryption on our website and secure
                        password protocols for our server access. However,
                        please remember that no transmission over the internet
                        is 100% secure.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-4'>
                        5. YOUR PRIVACY RIGHTS (POPIA)
                    </h2>
                    <p class='mb-4'>
                        Under the Protection of Personal Information Act
                        (POPIA), you have the right to:
                    </p>
                    <ul class='list-disc pl-6 space-y-2'>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Access:</strong> Request a copy of the personal
                            information we hold about you.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Correction:</strong> Request that we update or
                            correct any of your information.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Deletion:</strong> Request that we delete your
                            personal information (subject to our legal obligation
                            to keep tax/invoice records for 5 years).
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class='mt-4'>
                        To exercise these rights, please contact our Information
                        Officer at <a
                            href='mailto:jacob@apexcorporate.co.za'
                            class='text-primary hover:underline'
                            >jacob@apexcorporate.co.za</a
                        >.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-4'>6. COOKIES</h2>
                    <p>
                        We may use cookies and similar tracking technologies
                        (like web beacons and pixels) to access or store
                        information. This helps us analyze web traffic and
                        improve your browsing experience. You can refuse the use
                        of cookies by adjusting your browser settings.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-4'>
                        7. UPDATES TO THIS POLICY
                    </h2>
                    <p>
                        We may update this privacy policy from time to time. The
                        updated version will be indicated by an updated
                        "Revised" date and the updated version will be effective
                        as soon as it is accessible.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-4'>8. CONTACT US</h2>
                    <p class='mb-4'>
                        If you have questions or comments about this policy, you
                        may contact us at:
                    </p>
                    <address class='not-italic'>
                        <strong>Apex Corporate Solutions</strong><br />
                        (A division of Playhouse Media Group)<br />
                        Email: <a
                            href='mailto:jacob@apexcorporate.co.za'
                            class='text-primary hover:underline'
                            >jacob@apexcorporate.co.za</a
                        ><br />
                        Web: <a
                            href='https://www.apexcorporate.co.za'
                            class='text-primary hover:underline'
                            >www.apexcorporate.co.za</a
                        >
                    </address>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
